f:["$","span",null,{"className":"font-body font-default font-m neutral-on-background-medium mt-8 mb-12","style":{"lineHeight":"175%"},"children":"One key challenge was balancing the need for flexibility with the desire to maintain design consistency. The solution involved creating well-defined design tokens and establishing clear guidelines for when and how components could be customized. Additionally, setting up effective collaboration workflows between designers and developers using Figma and Git was a learning experience that greatly improved the process."}]
